  <description><![CDATA[<h3>Annotation Plugin.</h3>
    <em>This a code annotation plugin, it via AI server automatic annotation for Project,
    include developer language for it, for example: Java C++ Python and so on.</em>]]></description>
  <!-- Product and plugin compatibility requirements.
